 time</a></h3><div class="pb-20 font-polysans text-11 lg:text-12"><time dateTime="2024-05-03T17:41:27.349Z" class="duet--article--timestamp font-polysans text-12"> <!-- -->May 3, 2024, 5:41 PM UTC</time></div></li><li class="relative pb-20 pl-24 last:pb-0 lg:pl-28 [&amp;&gt;div]:border-b [&amp;&gt;div]:border-black/30 [&amp;&gt;div]:last:border-b-0 [&amp;&gt;div]:last:border-l-0"><div class="absolute -left-10 top-0 h-20 w-20 rounded-full border border-black bg-black lg:top-8"></div><div class="absolute left-0 top-0 h-full border-l border-l-black lg:top-8"></div><h3 class="mb-10 font-polysans text-22 font-medium leading-100 -tracking-1 selection:bg-franklin-20 lg:text-34"><a class="hover:border-b" href="/2024/4/30/24145853/so-whats-next-for-teslas-superchargers">So what’s next for Tesla’s Superchargers?</a></h3><div class="pb-20 font-polysans text-11 lg:text-12"><time dateTime="2024-04-30T22:51:56.145Z" class="duet--article--timestamp font-polysans text-12"> <!-- -->Apr 30, 2024, 10:51 PM UTC</time></div></li><li class="relative pb-20 pl-24 last:pb-0 lg:pl-28 [&amp;&gt;div]:border-b [&amp;&gt;div]:border-black/30 [&amp;&gt;div]:last:border-b-0 [&amp;&gt;div]:last:border-l-0"><div class="absolute -left-10 top-0 h-20 w-20 rounded-full border border-black bg-black lg:top-8"></div><div class="absolute left-0 top-0 h-full border-l border-l-black lg:top-8"></div><h3 class="mb-10 font-polysans text-22 font-medium leading-100 -tracking-1 selection:bg-franklin-20 lg:text-34"><a class="hover:border-b" href="/2024/4/30/24145621/tesla-layoff-supercharger-ev-charging-nacs-elon-musk">Tesla layoffs hit Supercharger team just as it’s poised to take over EV charging</a></h3><div class="pb-20 font-polysans text-11 lg:text-12"><time dateTime="2024-04-30T19:42:04.144Z" class="duet--article--timestamp font-polysans text-12"> <!-- -->Apr 30, 2024, 7:42 PM UTC</time></div></li><li class="relative pb-20 pl-24 last:pb-0 lg:pl-28 [&amp;&gt;div]:border-b [&amp;&gt;div]:border-black/30 [&amp;&g